attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes & Gardens - Wine Country Group
Better Homes & Gardens - Wine Country Group

data.description: CHALET-STYLE FIXER UPPER on a half acre+ lot!  Come & invest your sweat equity to turn this into the chalet-style home of your dreams! This tri-level home offers so much living space with a large main level featuring soaring wood-beamed ceilings, a woodstove set on a brick hearth, open kitchen & dining area, and a wrap around deck. Also on the main level is a spacious bedroom, full bathroom & laundry room.  Upstairs is a loft area - ideal for an office or lounge space, plus two bedrooms that share a full bathroom with stall shower. The lower level enjoys it's own private entrance, has a wide open floor plan with potential to create an additional living/sleeping/game room space, plus plumbing to add a kitchenette, has an attached full bathroom with stall shower and makes for a perfect family room, guest space, or even potential income opportunity! Set on an oversized lot and tucked under the beautiful oaks, there's room to improve the raised bed garden area and to create the yard you have been envisioning! There is a large storage room attached to the carport to add to the convenience.  Desirable location just moments from the local golf course & clubhouse, market, coffee shops, community lake & swimming pool, tennis courts & more!
